  "description": "Use when serializing Apex objects to JSON strings or deserializing JSON responses into Apex types \u2014 especially for callout payloads, integration parsing, and controlling null field output. Trigger keywords: 'suppress null fields JSON Apex', 'deserialize JSON into Apex class', 'JSON parse unknown shape', 'TypeException JSON deserialize', 'JSONGenerator streaming'. NOT for REST endpoint response shaping (use apex-rest-services), NOT for Apex remote actions returning JSON to LWC.",
